'''默克尔神经末梢'''（英文：Merkel nerve ending），又称'''默克尔触觉盘'''（Merkel's tactile disk）或'''默克尔盘'''（Merkel's disk），是一种缓慢调节的[[力學感受器|力学感受器]]，位于[[表皮基底层|表皮基底层]]与[[毛囊|毛囊]]中<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Mechanoreceptors Specialized to Receive Tactile Information|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10895/|last=Purves|first=Dale|last2=Augustine|first2=George J.|date=2001|journal=Neuroscience. 2nd edition|language=en|last3=Fitzpatrick|first3=David|last4=Katz|first4=Lawrence C.|last5=LaMantia|first5=Anthony-Samuel|last6=McNamara|first6=James O.|last7=Williams|first7=S. Mark|access-date=2021-02-21|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506132909/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK10895/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Merkel's tactile disk|url=https://dictionary.apa.org/|accessdate=2021-02-21|work=|publisher=APA Dictionary of Psychology|language=en|archive-date=2018-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180427011428/https://dictionary.apa.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Current understanding of Merkel cells, touch reception and the skin|author=Zdenek Halata, Milos Grim & Klaus I Baumann|url=https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.1586/edm.09.70|journal=Expert Rev. Dermatol|issue=1|year=2010|volume=5|page=109–116}}</ref>。默克尔神经末梢以德国科学家[[弗里德里希·西格蒙德·默克尔|弗里德里希·西格蒙德·默克尔]]的名字命名。它们能感知机械压力和位置，也能通过深层静态触碰进行特征感知，譬如感知形状和边缘<ref name=":0" />。

[[默克尔细胞|默克尔细胞]]位于[[表皮基底层|表皮基底层]]，储存[[血清素|血清素]]，并在感知压力时释放至相应的[[神经末梢|神经末梢]]<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Merkel disc is a serotonergic synapse in the epidermis for transmitting tactile signals in mammals|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/113/37/E5491|last=Chang|first=Weipang|last2=Kanda|first2=Hirosato|date=2016-09-13|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=37|doi=10.1073/pnas.1610176113|volume=113|pages=E5491–E5500|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmid=27573850|last3=Ikeda|first3=Ryo|last4=Ling|first4=Jennifer|last5=DeBerry|first5=Jennifer J.|last6=Gu|first6=Jianguo G.|access-date=2021-02-21|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301171205/https://www.pnas.org/content/113/37/E5491|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每个末梢都由一个默克尔细胞与一个邻近神经终端的组成，因此被称为“默克尔细胞-[[神经突|神经突]]复合体（Merkel cell–neurite complex）”或默克尔触觉盘<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Merkel cells and neurons keep in touch|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4312710/|last=Woo|first=Seung-Hyun|last2=Lumpkin|first2=Ellen A.|date=2015-2|journal=Trends in cell biology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.tcb.2014.10.003|volume=25|pages=74–81|issn=0962-8924|pmc=4312710|pmid=25480024|last3=Patapoutian|first3=Ardem}}</ref>。单个[[传入神经纤维|传入神经纤维]]可支配约90个此种神经末梢。

